StringValues.16: You see a piece of paper, with illegible writing.  The author used a strange russet ink, and wrote in what seems to be the swirling patterns of the Falatacot.
StringValues.14: Use this item to read it.

Pages.Text: This is hastily written Falatacot,  You cannot understand it.
